{"tid":2125694,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"選舉主任DQ民主派或被西方以《全球馬格尼茨基人權問責法》制裁？","createTime":"2020-07-26T10:45:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-30T19:47:35.000Z","uid":2054,"like":32,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"1ebeddc0e1c81d1357dac7a0c5cb606bcc53677a","tid":2125694,"uid":2054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-26T10:45:52.000Z","msg":"Pompeo講到明睇到實立法會選舉<br />\n比整個西方自由世界制裁唔係講笑<br />\n成世留係大灣區用崑崙銀行<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GtBymMP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGtBymMP.png&h=71cf2aaa&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2gqnZyw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2gqnZyw.png&h=f8f56bfa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n法案具體內容包括：<br />\n<br />\n該法案賦予總統權力禁止入境、凍結相關個人或組織的資產。其制裁的對象包括：<br />\n<br />\n負責執行非法處決、酷刑或其他嚴重<span class=\"red\">侵害人權、並妨礙爭取人權的任何人士，包括不分官階高低的政府人員</span>；<br />\n有嚴重貪污受賄或腐敗行為的任何人士；<br />\n為上述人士轉移非法收入或提賄款到外地的任何人士；<br />\n為上述人士提供便利、財政或技術支援的任何人士。<br />\n<br />\n美國《全球馬格尼茨基人權問責法》2012年在眾議院通過，2015年在參議院通過，2016年附加在年度《國防授權法》中。該法案授權美國政府對違反人權及國外顯著腐敗人士實施制裁，例如<span class=\"red\">禁止入境、凍結並禁止官員在美國的財產交易。</span><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">英國</span>政府本周稍早前也以馬格尼茨基人權法為法律基礎，宣布首批全球人權制裁名單。<br />\n<br />\n此外，先後通過了本國版本的馬格尼茨基法案的國家包括：毗鄰俄羅斯的<span class=\"red\">拉脫維亞、立陶宛和愛沙尼亞；加拿大和科索沃</span>。<span class=\"red\">澳大利亞、法國、瑞典、荷蘭</span>的類似法案正在審議，<span class=\"red\">歐盟</span>去年12月承諾將出台相關法案，因新冠疫情爆發而暫停。"},{"pid":"5c3e6d077ff3c9bb8674762d8abd11f200ffadfb","tid":2125694,"uid":284432,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-26T10:55:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4d1987266d51483b7eacf5fe02994dc2f9dac58f","tid":2125694,"uid":127575,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T15:12:36.000Z","msg":"正呀 !!! 選舉主任一世用崑崙銀行 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a36088aaadf44a96c4fee4de2159aa6961747fef","tid":2125694,"uid":127575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T15:50:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ac082750130ec5d1f1a2aab406a9937ccc48b10","tid":2125694,"uid":306914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T15:56:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ed055ccd8eada4fa9e127231d78d555e224e19b","tid":2125694,"uid":2054,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"4d1987266d51483b7eacf5fe02994dc2f9dac58f","tid":2125694,"uid":127575,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T15:12:36.000Z","msg":"正呀 !!! 選舉主任一世用崑崙銀行 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T06:12:06.000Z","msg":"行政會議成員成首批用戶<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b73c19c80c2c959589c16fe6708989825be5101","tid":2125694,"uid":4917,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"2ed055ccd8eada4fa9e127231d78d555e224e19b","tid":2125694,"uid":2054,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"4d1987266d51483b7eacf5fe02994dc2f9dac58f","tid":2125694,"uid":127575,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T15:12:36.000Z","ms